ADDITIONAL NOTICE — SYNTHETIC DATA AND DECISION SUPPORT

CertMesh is a workforce learning / certification-management DECISION-SUPPORT
demonstrator, NOT a system of record. All learner records, work signals,
certification ontologies, knowledge documents and example cases in this
repository are SYNTHETIC and ILLUSTRATIVE — they are fabricated for
demonstration only, use invented identifiers (e.g. L-1001, EMP-001, TEAM-A),
and are not a substitute for an organisation's official certification
requirements or HR records. No real personal data or PII is present in this
repository. Manager-facing insights are aggregated and thresholded by design
and must not be used to make decisions about identifiable individuals.
